body_html: @fenderrex I'm not sure I understand your question. The default behavior when name=None is to add a prefix of "import" (perhaps with a suffix of "_1", "_2", etc. if that prefix has already been used). If there's a particular change you'd suggest, feel free to open a new issue describing it, and we'll take a look!
